sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as External Client
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Gateway (Envoy)<br/>443/TCP TLS Terminate
    participant EnvoyFilter as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz + Lua
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Backend as Backend Service<br/>(via HTTPRoute)
    participant User as Platform Admin
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCWebhook as DSC Webhook<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompRegistry as Component Registry
    participant CompReconciler as Component Reconciler
    participant OTEL as OpenTelemetry<br/>Collector
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>8889/TCP HTTPS
    participant Tempo as Tempo<br/>4317/TCP gRPC

    rect rgb(230, 245, 255)
        Note over Client,Backend: Flow 1: Platform Ingress (LoadBalancer Mode)
        Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>TLS Terminate (GatewayConfig cert)
        Gateway->>EnvoyFilter: ext_authz check<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
        EnvoyFilter->>AuthProxy: OAuth2/OIDC credentials<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS (insecureSkipVerify)
        AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: x-auth-request-access-token<br/>x-auth-request-user headers
        EnvoyFilter->>Backend: Lua forwards Bearer token<br/>via HTTPRoute matching
        Backend-->>Client: Response (via Gateway)
    end

    rect rgb(255, 243, 224)
        Note over Client,Route: Flow 2: Legacy Dashboard Redirect
        Client->>Route: HTTPS/443<br/>edge TLS (legacy hostname)
        Route->>Route: nginx 301 redirect<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        Route-->>Client: 301 Redirect to<br/>rh-ai.{cluster-domain}
        Client->>Gateway: HTTPS/443<br/>(follows redirect, Flow 1)
    end

    rect rgb(224, 242, 224)
        Note over User,CompReconciler: Flow 3: Component Provisioning
        User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update DSC CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS, Bearer token
        K8sAPI->>DSCWebhook: Validation + Defaulting<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS, cert-manager TLS
        DSCWebhook-->>K8sAPI: Admitted
        K8sAPI-->>DSCCtrl: Watch event
        DSCCtrl->>CompRegistry: Iterate component handlers
        CompRegistry->>K8sAPI: Create component CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
        K8sAPI-->>CompReconciler: Watch event (component CR)
        CompReconciler->>K8sAPI: Apply kustomize manifests<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS, SA token
    end

    rect rgb(242, 224, 242)
        Note over Backend,Tempo: Flow 4: Observability Pipeline
        Backend->>OTEL: Metrics + Traces<br/>4317/TCP gRPC, 4318/TCP HTTP
        OTEL->>Prometheus: Export metrics<br/>8889/TCP HTTPS (serving-cert)
        OTEL->>Tempo: Export traces<br/>4317/TCP gRPC TLS
    end
